port1/hi/football/teams/d/dundee_utd/7463080.stm|title=Dixon delights in Dundee Utd move |date=23 June 2008|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2008-06-23}}</ref>\n|}\n\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Dundee United to Dundee===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size:95%\"\n|-\n! Date\n! Player\n! Fee\n|-\n| {{0}}{{0}} {{0}}{{0}}{{0}} 1947 || {{flagicon|SCO}} [[George Mackay (footballer)|George Mackay]] || ''Unknown''<ref name=\"history\"/>\n|-\n| {{0}}{{0}} {{0}}{{0}}{{0}} 1948 || {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Jack Court]] || ''Unknown''<ref name=\"history\"/>\n|-\n| {{0}}{{0}} {{0}}{{0}}{{0}} 1971 || {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Ian Scott (footballer, born 1946)|Ian Scott]] || ''Unknown''\n|-\n| {{0}}{{0}} {{0}}{{0}}{{0}} 1977 || {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Billy Williamson (footballer, born 1952)|Billy Williamson]] ||''Unknown''\n|-\n| 13 Dec 1986 || {{flagicon|IRL}} [[Tommy Coyne]] || \u00a375,000<ref name=\"coyne\">{{cite web|url=http://www.dirtyarab.pwp.blueyonder.co.uk/Player%20a-z/Coyne%20T.htm |title=Glenrothes Arabs Player A to Z: Tommy Coyne |publisher=Glenrothes Arabs |accessdate=2008-02-18 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081015114417/http://www.dirtyarab.pwp.blueyonder.co.uk/Player%20a-z/Coyne%20T.htm |archivedate=15 October 2008 }}</ref>\n|-\n| {{0}}{{0}} {{0}}{{0}}{{0}} 1995 || {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Roy McBain]] ||''Unknown''\n|-\n| 3 Jun 1997 || {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Jim McInally]] || Free<ref name=\"mcinally\">{{cite web|url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=5144|title=The Internet Soccer Database: Jim McInally|accessdate=2008-02-18|publisher=Soccerbase}}</ref>\n|-\n| 5 Jan 2019 || {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Craig Curran]] ||''Free''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/46772020|title=Dundee: Craig Curran swaps Dundee United for Tayside rivals|date=5 January 2019|via=www.bbc.co.uk}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n{{col-end}}\n\n===Complete list===\nIn addition, other players have played for both clubs without moving directly between them. A list of all