ns]]||bgcolor=00008B|<center><span style=\"color:white;\">'''2 \u2013 1'''</span></center>||10,747||[[Nacho Novo|Novo]], [[Steve Lovell|Lovell]]||[[Billy Dodds|Dodds]]\n|-\n| 11 Apr 2004 || [[Scottish Premier League|Premier League]] ||[[Tannadice Park|Tannadice]]|| style=\"background:dimGrey;\"|<center><span style=\"color:white;\">'''2 \u2013 2'''</span></center>||9,571|| [[Steve Lovell|Lovell]], [[Steven Milne|Milne]] || [[Billy Dodds|Dodds]] (2)\n|-\n| 15 Aug 2004 || [[Scottish Premier League|Premier League]] ||[[Tannadice Park|Tannadice]]||bgcolor=00008B|<center><span style=\"color:white;\">'''1 \u2013 2'''</span></center>||11,118|| [[Steve Lovell|Lovell]], [[John Sutton (footballer)|Sutton]] || [[Alan Archibald|Archibald]]\n|-\n| 6 Nov 2004 || [[Scottish Premier League|Premier League]] ||[[Dens Park|Dens]]||bgcolor=00008B|<center><span style=\"color:white;\">'''1 \u2013 0'''</span></center>||9,845||[[John Sutton (footballer)|Sutton]]||\n|-\n| 29 Jan 2005 || [[Scottish Premier League|Premier League]] ||[[Tannadice Park|Tannadice]]|| style=\"background:dimGrey;\"|<center><span style=\"color:white;\">'''2 \u2013 2'''</span></center>||12,703|| [[Tam McManus|McManus]], [[Steve Lovell|Lovell]] || [[Stuart Duff|Duff]], [[Jim McIntyre (footballer)|McIntyre]]\n|-\n| 30 Apr 2005 || [[Scottish Premier League|Premier League]] ||[[Dens Park|Dens]]||bgcolor=FF7700|<center><span style=\"color:black;\">'''1 \u2013 2'''</span></center>||11,263||[[Steve Lovell|Lovell]]||[[Mark Wilson (Scottish footballer)|Wilson]], [[Jim McIntyre (footballer)|McIntyre]]\n|-\n| 19 Aug 2012 || [[Scottish Premier League|Premier League]] ||[[Tannadice Park|Tannadice]]||bgcolor=FF7700|<center><span style=\"color:black;\">'''3 \u2013 0'''</span></center>||13,538|| ||[[Gavin Gunning|Gunning]], [[Johnny Russell (footballer)|Russell]] (2)\n|-\n| 9 Dec 2012 || [[Scottish Premier League|Premier League]] ||[[Dens Park|Dens]]||bgcolor=FF7700|<center><span style=\"color:black;\">'''0 \u2013 3'''</span></center